Interface IObdInfoServiceNeeds

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IServiceNeeds
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ISwcObdInfoServiceNeeds

    public interface IObdInfoServiceNeeds
extends IEntity, IServiceNeeds
    IObdInfoServiceNeeds: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Specifies the abstract needs of a compoment or module on the configuration of OBD Services in relation to a given InfoType (OBD Service 09), which is supported by this component or module.
